OL,3,CNorthern cities will 'remain poorly
OL,4,Cserved' by rail, Government advisers
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FImportant routes between Birmingham
OL,8,Fand north-west England will "remain
OL,9,Fpoorly served" by rail because of the
OL,10,Fcurtailment of HS2, Government
OL,11,Fadvisers have warned.
OL,13,FThe National Infrastructure Commission
OL,14,F(NIC) said a "do nothing" scenario
OL,15,Fnorth of Handsacre Junction,
OL,16,FStaffordshire ` where HS2 is now
OL,17,Fplanned to stop ` is "not sustainable".
