OL,3,CNorthern cities will 'remain poorly
OL,4,Cserved' by rail, Government advisers
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FThe review found there is "a number of
OL,8,Fspecific bottlenecks" between
OL,9,FManchester and Birmingham, stating
OL,10,Fthat the West Coast Main Line is
OL,11,F"already running at a higher intensity
OL,12,Fof operation than major fast lines in
OL,13,Fother European countries", which
OL,14,Fnegatively affects reliability.
OL,16,FIn October last year, Prime Minister
OL,17,FRishi Sunak cancelled the plan to
OL,18,Fextend HS2 between the West Midlands
OL,19,Fand Manchester amid spiralling costs.
