OL,4,Cserved' by rail, Government advisers
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FHe acknowledged that schemes such as
OL,8,Fthe Midlands Rail Hub and Northern
OL,9,FPowerhouse Rail "might address" some
OL,10,Fconnectivity concerns, but "there does
OL,11,Fremain a critical gap in the links
OL,12,Fbetween Birmingham, Manchester and the
OL,13,FNorth West."
OL,15,FMr Sunak made his HS2 announcement
OL,16,Falongside the publication of a
OL,17,FGovernment document named Network
OL,18,FNorth, setting out #36 billion of
OL,19,Fimprovements to road, rail and bus
OL,20,Fservices across the UK.
