OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FThe review also found that the current
OL,8,Frate of a 30% annual increase in new
OL,9,Fpublic electric vehicle chargers being
OL,10,Finstalled must be maintained to hit
OL,11,Fthe Government's target of 300,000 by
OL,12,F2030.
OL,14,FThis will "become more challenging in
OL,15,Flater years" with the required annual
OL,16,Ftotal reaching around 75,000 in 2029,
OL,17,Fthe commission warned.
