OL,7,FThe report said: "Government must
OL,8,Fcontinue to address any barriers to
OL,9,Fdeployment, such as issues in securing
OL,10,Ftimely connection to the electricity
OL,11,Fnetwork due to capacity limitations
OL,12,Fand slow progress in creating more
OL,13,Fcapacity.
OL,15,F"With less than six years left to meet
OL,16,Fits ambition, Government and Ofgem
OL,17,Fmust address these barriers to
OL,18,Fdeployment."
